#: ../../../power/shutdown-debugging.rst:4
msgid "Debugging Kernel Shutdown Hangs with pstore"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../power/shutdown-debugging.rst:7
msgid "Overview"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../power/shutdown-debugging.rst:8
msgid ""
"If the system hangs while shutting down, the kernel logs may need to be "
"retrieved to debug the issue."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../power/shutdown-debugging.rst:11
msgid ""
"On systems that have a UART available, it is best to configure the kernel to "
"use this UART for kernel console output."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../power/shutdown-debugging.rst:14
msgid ""
"If a UART isn't available, the ``pstore`` subsystem provides a mechanism to "
"persist this data across a system reset, allowing it to be retrieved on the "
"next boot."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../power/shutdown-debugging.rst:19
msgid "Kernel Configuration"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../power/shutdown-debugging.rst:20
msgid ""
"To enable ``pstore`` and enable saving kernel ring buffer logs, set the "
"following kernel configuration options:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../power/shutdown-debugging.rst:23
msgid "``CONFIG_PSTORE=y``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../power/shutdown-debugging.rst:24
msgid "``CONFIG_PSTORE_CONSOLE=y``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../power/shutdown-debugging.rst:26
msgid ""
"Additionally, enable a backend to store the data. Depending upon your "
"platform some potential options include:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../power/shutdown-debugging.rst:29
msgid "``CONFIG_EFI_VARS_PSTORE=y``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../power/shutdown-debugging.rst:30
msgid "``CONFIG_PSTORE_RAM=y``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../power/shutdown-debugging.rst:31
msgid "``CONFIG_CHROMEOS_PSTORE=y``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../power/shutdown-debugging.rst:32
msgid "``CONFIG_PSTORE_BLK=y``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../power/shutdown-debugging.rst:35
msgid "Kernel Command-line Parameters"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../power/shutdown-debugging.rst:36
msgid "Add these parameters to your kernel command line:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../power/shutdown-debugging.rst:38
msgid "``printk.always_kmsg_dump=Y``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../power/shutdown-debugging.rst:39
msgid "Forces the kernel to dump the entire message buffer to pstore during"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../power/shutdown-debugging.rst:40
msgid "shutdown"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../power/shutdown-debugging.rst:41
msgid "``efi_pstore.pstore_disable=N``"
